metadata.name: Reading a book #823
metadata.description:
The formal structure of a book is beautiful by itself, but its aesthetic is the tacit atmosphere within which events take place in a story.

The WebGL real-time animation sets up an initial grid based on the fxhash. The grid cells get subdivided into another grid and the resulting cells become filled with pixels in color (~33%) or black and white (~66%).
The colored pixels come in 3 different coloring styles.
- Big Palette (~49%)
- Small Palette (~49%)
- Monochrome [b/w] (~2%)
4 noise algorithms modify the pixels of selected grid cells while at the same time 4 reset algorithms reassemble the initial image. The selected cells switch over time.

metadata.name: Flores del Mal #2 #58
metadata.description:
"Flores del Mal 2" is another take into the world of flowers and a solitary moon. The inspiration came from nature and the strange beauty of "Les fleurs du mal" by French author Charles Baudelaire.

Features
- 10 possible backgrounds
- 3 possible flower colors
- 3 possible moon colors
- 2 possible frame colors
- 1 to 3 levels of line density

metadata.name: Visa to the stars #477
metadata.description:
Generative space scenes with an illustrative look.

Use the capture functions to export in big after opening it in its own window, the artwork is full of details.

Press SPACE to show/hide the menu

Control the camera and explore the scene with :
- Mouse Left : Rotate
- Mouse Right : Pan
- Mouse Middle : Zoom

I wrote an article about the project, with a technical breakdown of the piece at https://ulucode.com/wp/visa-to-the-stars/


Decent GPU REQUIRED, you can tune the performances with the "Quality" setting in the menu.
Better performances with Chrome.

Keyboard shortcuts:
SPACE : show/hide menu
A : toggle anti-aliasing
C : take a capture of the ccurrently selected resolution
R : reset camera position/orientation
S : display stats
P : pause animation

metadata.name: Flowers of the noise dimension #1
metadata.description:
Come. Sit next to to me. Finally you are here. Please drink of the tea of this special flowers, don´t worry, nothing bad is going to happen to you. Yeah that´s it. Good. Don´t fear now, yes the things you are seeing now are real, you see now the true shape of the dimension, the noise arround us. The noise is what allows us to breath, to eat to exist. 

GLSL shader. One buffer. Full generative . Not a single png.
